---
// src/components/sections/Problem.astro
---

<section class="relative border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.04)] py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 md:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Title column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-[var(--color-accent)] uppercase">
          La realidad operativa
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight">
          El papel y el desorden manual te están costando dinero.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          Los sistemas no fallan por falta de botones llamativos. Fallan cuando la complejidad operativa supera tu estructura de trabajo, o cuando sigues dependiendo de planillas de Excel aisladas y registros manuales vulnerables a errores humanos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem cards column -->
      <div class="space-y-6 lg:col-span-7">
        <!-- Problem Card 1 -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.01)] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[rgba(50,255,126,0.2)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.02)] md:p-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-start">
            <span class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[rgba(239,68,68,0.1)] text-red-400 font-bold font-mono text-lg border border-[rgba(239,68,68,0.15)] group-hover:bg-red-500 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300">
              01
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">
                Fuga Operativa por Tareas Manuales
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
                Tus empleados pasan horas copiando datos de un papel a otro o actualizando stock de forma manual. Cada hora dedicada a tareas mecánicas es tiempo perdido para generar valor o atender mejor a tus clientes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem Card 2 -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.01)] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[rgba(50,255,126,0.2)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.02)] md:p-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-start">
            <span class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[rgba(245,158,11,0.1)] text-amber-400 font-bold font-mono text-lg border border-[rgba(245,158,11,0.15)] group-hover:bg-amber-500 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300">
              02
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">
                Sistemas Rígidos y Enlatados
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
                El software genérico te obliga a forzar tus procesos para adaptarte a él. Al final, pagas licencias caras por sistemas complejos que nadie sabe usar completamente o que no resuelven tus dolores de raíz.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem Card 3 -->
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.01)] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[rgba(50,255,126,0.2)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.02)] md:p-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-start">
            <span class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[rgba(239,68,68,0.1)] text-red-400 font-bold font-mono text-lg border border-[rgba(239,68,68,0.15)] group-hover:bg-red-500 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300">
              03
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">
                Ventas Perdidas por Lentitud o Fricción
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
                Sin un e-commerce robusto ni respuestas automatizadas inmediatas por canales digitales, tus clientes se van con la competencia que sí les responde al instante y les facilita el pago inmediato.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
